        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Thus h(x), h(x+p*),...,h(x+ (p-1)p?) run over all of the residue classes modulo p' congruent to h(x) modulo p?. Since the h(x) themselves cover all the residue classes modulo p', this proves that h(O),...,h(p3 - 1) are distinct modulo p",
