        "id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2008_Solutions_2008s_page_005_23",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "For n < k + 1, all involutions are k-limited. By the previous paragraph, Fn,k is odd for n = 0, 1 and even for n =2,..., k+1.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5582310066126717,
          0.5872093021907335,
          0.9191729340438677,
