      {
        "id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2008_Solutions_2008s_page_005_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Let q = a/b be any rational number with gcd (a, b) = 1 and b > 0. For n any positive integer, we have",
        "bbox": [
          0.12781955462465844,
          0.7993551585561404,
